# crew-cli Development Roadmap

> Multi-agent coding CLI that orchestrates Aider, Gemini, Codex, Claude Code, and Cursor CLIs  
> **Status**: 🟢 Complete → Ready for Launch  
> **Timeline**: 7 days MVP, 21 days to public v0.1.0-alpha  

---

