### [x] 11. Shared Memory Broker + Hybrid Vector RAG ✓ 2026-03-01
- [x] Unified memory retrieval broker:
  - [x] merge AgentKeeper episodic memory + AgentMemory facts + Collections RAG.
  - [x] expose single ranked recall surface for CLI memory queries.
- [x] Shared memory root support:
  - [x] AgentKeeper now supports `CREW_MEMORY_DIR` for cross-tier/shared persistence.
- [x] Hybrid retrieval:
  - [x] added local vector-like ranking (hashed-vector cosine) blended with lexical TF-IDF.
  - [x] keeps fully local/offline operation (no external vector DB required).
- [x] CLI UX:
  - [x] `crew memory` defaults to broker mode (`--rag`), with `--no-rag`, `--include-code`, and `--path`.
- Acceptance criteria:
  - [x] broker returns cross-source hits (`agentkeeper`, `agent-memory`, `collections`).
  - [x] shared memory works across different working dirs when `CREW_MEMORY_DIR` is set.
  - [x] targeted tests + build pass.

